query:
SELECT f.id as favorite_id, f.propertyId, f.userId, u.name as user_name, p.address, p.county 
FROM favorites f 
LEFT JOIN users u ON f.userId = u.id 
LEFT JOIN properties p ON f.propertyId = p.id 
ORDER BY f.createdAt DESC
